  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Market Expansion & Business Development</p><p>• Identify and develop new business opportunities across the APAC region, focusing on industrial plant design and construction projects.</p><p>• Build and maintain strong relationships with clients, developers, investors, and key industry stakeholders.</p><p>• Drive end-to-end sales cycles, from prospecting to deal closure, ensuring successful project acquisitions.</p><p>• Strategic Partnerships & Client Engagement</p><p>• Collaborate closely with engineering, commercial, and project management teams to tailor solutions that meet client needs.</p><p>• Engage with multinational corporations (MNCs), government entities, and EPC project developers to position the company as a preferred contractor.</p><p>• Lead contract negotiations, bids, and proposals in line with market trends and client demands.</p>",
